<i>noun</i>: 충견 [충견] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>충견 [충견]</dt><br>
<dd>1. faithful dog</dd><br>
<dd>주인에게 충성스러운 개.</dd><br>
<dd>A dog that is very devoted to its owner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. minion; a cat's paw</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 자신이 모시는 사람에게 충성하는 앞잡이.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) Someone who is very loyal to the person he/she works under.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>